'''Irshalgad''' is a fortress located between [[Matheran]] and [[Panvel]] in [[Maharashtra]], [[India]]. It is a sister fort to [[Prabalgad]]. The area of the fort is not large but there are several water cisterns cut from the rock. The nearest village is Irshalwadi.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.giridarshan.com/forts/Irshalgad/Irshalgad2.html|title=Giridarshan Trekking|accessdate=2009-09-07}}</ref>

